# Agent playbook — bundle release and OpenSpec (local only)

Copy to **`AGENTS-LOCAL.md`** via `./snippets/bootstrap-maintainer-local.sh`. Gitignored. Do not commit.

## When to use this playbook

- Release or version the bundle (“bump version”, “prepare vX.Y.Z”, “update changelog”)
- Cut a git tag for cursor-dev-workflows
- Implement bundle features tracked in **`openspec/changes/<slug>/`**

For normal workflow routing, use [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md) and [which-workflow.md](which-workflow.md).

## Read order (release)

1. [docs/versioning.md](docs/versioning.md)
2. [CHANGELOG.md](CHANGELOG.md) — `## [Unreleased]`
3. [VERSION](VERSION)
4. Git diff / status

## Read order (feature work)

1. Gitignored [MAINTAINER.md](MAINTAINER.md) if present
2. Active change under `openspec/changes/<slug>/` — `proposal.md`, `design.md`, `tasks.md`
3. [docs/ai/openspec.md](docs/ai/openspec.md) and [overlays/lsi/docs/workflows/openspec-git-integration.md](overlays/lsi/docs/workflows/openspec-git-integration.md)
4. Canonical bundle specs: [docs/workflows/](docs/workflows/) + [overlays/lsi/](overlays/lsi/)

## OpenSpec (tracked)

- Changes: **`openspec/changes/<slug>/`**
- Config: [openspec/config.yaml](openspec/config.yaml)
- `/opsx:sync` → `openspec/specs/`
- `/opsx:archive` → `openspec/changes/archive/`

## Edit rules

- Changelog under `## [Unreleased]`; **Adopter action** subsection on MAJOR
- Update [VERSION](VERSION) only when cutting a release
- Never stage `MAINTAINER.md`, `AGENTS-LOCAL.md`, `.cursor/commands/`, or machine paths
- Commit `openspec/` with feature PRs when deltas change

## Suggested commit plan (user must explicitly ask)

1. `docs(changelog): note <summary>`
2. `chore(release): mark bundle vX.Y.Z`

Per [docs/workflows/commits-logical-order.md](docs/workflows/commits-logical-order.md).

## Tagging (only when user asks)

```bash
git tag -a vX.Y.Z -m "cursor-dev-workflows vX.Y.Z"
```

Do not push unless explicitly asked.

## Release steps

1. Work on release branch off `main`
2. Finalize `## [Unreleased]` → `## [X.Y.Z] - YYYY-MM-DD`
3. Set [VERSION](VERSION)
4. Commit when asked; tag when asked
5. Re-sync adopters per [MAINTAINER.md](MAINTAINER.md)

## Boundaries

- Docs-only repo — no `TEST_COMMAND` for bundle releases
- Do not duplicate release steps into tracked [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md)
- Do not run `adopt.py --target .` on the bundle
